name: Hecate
description:
>ripped out of her throne, erased from the history
>the queen now lives in the shadows
>guiding warriors to victory and hunters to their prey
>revealing the secrets of nature and magic for the women who seek freedom
>justice be over those who scandalize the lady's name!
>shame be over them, may their lies be revealed, may they be seen as slanderous and perverse;
>for they have silenced a women out of fear to be revealed on their mistakes
>long live, queen Hecate!
>may your wisdom be every day more vast, and your beauty, every day brigter!

A story about the world? Yes, yes, we know one.
This is how the journey of the artists to show their vision about the Greek gods and their forms begins.

#cryptoamigues #CryptOlimpianos
